title: #75 - Logan Paul Humiliated & Roseanne Loses It
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast Ethan brings to you the worst tweet of all time thanks to the master maverick himself- Logan Paul. Additionally we talk about Roseanne's "apology", watch a bizarre 1990's PSA, play Know Your Meme ft. Skippy, and a whole lot more!
